{"id":3709,"title":"[The Oncologic and Palliative Network Landshut: a problem-solving approach to oncological and palliative care in structurally weak rural areas, with special emphasis on outpatient and inpatient networking].","abstract":"The Oncologic and Palliative Network Landshut is a problem-solving approach to structurally weak rural areas to improve an adequate care of critically ill patients, especially by a close involvement of outpatient and inpatient care providers. These networks not only improve the medical and nursing care of patients, but can also be cost-effective.","date":"2014-11-24","categories":"Neoplasms","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25417445","annotations":[{"name":"Oncology","weight":0.780863,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oncology"},{"name":"Palliative care","weight":0.632564,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Palliative_care"},{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.558923,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"Nursing","weight":0.46009,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nursing"},{"name":"Outpatient","weight":0.185505,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Outpatient"},{"name":"Rural area","weight":0.18053,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rural_area"},{"name":"Inpatient","weight":0.175148,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inpatient"},{"name":"Intensive-care medicine","weight":0.152154,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intensive-care_medicine"},{"name":"Inpatient care","weight":0.135948,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inpatient_care"},{"name":"Landshut","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Landshut"},{"name":"Computer network","weight":0.018953,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_network"},{"name":"Structure","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Structure"}]}
